{'text': 'We had an unforgettable time celebrating my wife’s birthday at The Elephant Room. From the moment we walked in, the atmosphere was warm and inviting, setting the perfect tone for the evening. The cocktails were nothing short of extraordinary each one crafted with creativity and deep-rooted inspiration from Singapore’s culture.

A special mention to Jeevan, a well-known mixologist in Singapore, whose passion and expertise truly elevated our experience. His recommendations were spot on, and every drink told a story. The attention to detail, the balance of flavors, and the overall hospitality made this celebration even more special.

Thank you to the team at The Elephant Room for a fantastic night! Highly recommended for anyone looking for a unique and memorable cocktail experience.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

